    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Also note that Scala extends String with a number of methods (via implicit conversion to a WrappedString brought in by Predef) so you could also do the following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>val formattedString = \"Hello %s, isn't %s cool?\".format(\"Ivan\", \"Scala\")\n</code></pre>\n"
