    "body" : "<p>You can use this;</p>\n\n<pre><code>String.format(\"%1$s %2$s %2$s %3$s\", \"a\", \"b\", \"c\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Output: </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>a b b c</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
